name: RNR_001 - BLUE OAK
description:
RNR_001 - BLUE OAK
The formative, analog feedback oak tree - life, art, color and sound fully integrated. 

Analog video feedback loop using an RCA T09085 television and a Samsung SCL810 camcorder with built-in digital mirror effect, with a Videonics MX-1. Minor digital color correction. Recorded straight into OBS, with some digital loss....however, this further reinforces the live-stream creation of the work. 

Music created live on a THERE'S NOTHING WEIRD ABOUT IT stream in 2021.
